room_title: Escape room "The Study" by NC Escape in Raleigh - Durham
review: This was awesome! We had two teams and we competed in The Study room at the same time. This definitely a great place for team building! I loved it!

room_title: Escape room "The Study" by NC Escape in Raleigh - Durham
review: We've done 15 or so escape rooms in the area and this place is great. We did Ex Machina and The Study back to back and beat them both! They are both a good challenge which made them fun.
